(164, 'widget_bx-item-about', 'a:3:{s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;i:3;a:2:{s:5:"title";s:11:"Who we are?";s:7:"excerpt";s:512:"WebKiDunia is a platform for you to enhance and digitalised your business. We basically deal in website development and online marketing. Bulk SMS, promotional ads &amp; graphic designing are some of the other fields we deal in. Our services list is an ever increasing process. And so are our happy customers.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nIf you decide to start a business, let WebKiDunia help you.\r\nIf you want to promote yourself, let WebKiDunia help you.\r\nIf you are in need of any sort of digitalization, let WebKiDunia help you.";}i:4;a:2:{s:5:"title";s:11:"What we do?";s:7:"excerpt";s:436:"WebKiDunia helps digitalise you. Be it a school website or an e-commerce website. We are ready to get you digitalised in any form you want and any time you demand.\r\n\r\nWebKiDunia team consist of enhanced techies, experienced data analysts and vivid content writers. We already have a century of satisfied customers and ever increasing clients.\r\n\r\nWebKiDunia is an initiative to turn the digital India dream into a real digitalised India.";}}', 'yes'),
(165, 'widget_bx-item-testimonials', 'a:8:{s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;i:3;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:18:"Mr. Sudesh Sangate";s:6:"avatar";s:67:"http://webkidunia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SUDESH-Sangate.png";s:11:"testimonial";s:141:"Informative websites are all monotonous. Thanks to WebKiDunia for putting in tonnes of creativity. Looking ahead to work with you more often.";s:8:"btn_text";s:32:"Director - Pioneer Public School";s:7:"btn_url";s:34:"http://pioneerpublicschooldws.org/";}i:4;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:18:"Mr. Sudesh Sangate";s:6:"avatar";s:67:"http://webkidunia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SUDESH-Sangate.png";s:11:"testimonial";s:188:"It was one of the shortest deadline. Plus we were quite low on funds. But then we had WebKiDunia! Project before time and under our budget. The best that we could have had. Thank you guys!";s:8:"btn_text";s:29:"Secretary - M. P. Soft Tennis";s:7:"btn_url";s:24:"http://mpsofttennis.org/";}i:6;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:15:"Mr. Ashok Joshi";s:6:"avatar";s:77:"http://webkidunia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Ebenezer-School-Director.png";s:11:"testimonial";s:139:"Incredible, fast &amp; user friendly. Not just the faculty but the students are in an instant love with the features! Thank You WebKiDunia.";s:8:"btn_text";s:32:"Director - Ebenezer S. S. School";s:7:"btn_url";s:32:"http://www.ebenezerssschool.org/";}i:8;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:15:"Mr. P. N Tiwari";s:6:"avatar";s:62:"http://webkidunia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/PN-Tiwari.png";s:11:"testimonial";s:151:"It took us a while to find someone who could accomplish what we needed for the website. And it was a total and utter pleasure to work with WebKiDuniya.";s:8:"btn_text";s:31:"Director - Saraswati Gyan Peeth";s:7:"btn_url";s:33:"http://www.saraswatigyanpeeth.in/";}i:9;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:17:"Mr. M. S. Chouhan";s:6:"avatar";s:65:"http://webkidunia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/M.-S-CHOUHAN.png";s:11:"testimonial";s:80:"Incredible efforts by the designers. Can''t think anything less than WebKiDuniya!";s:8:"btn_text";s:28:"Director - Vedant Industries";s:7:"btn_url";s:27:"http://vedantindustries.in/";}i:11;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:15:"Mr. Rajan Arora";s:6:"avatar";s:84:"http://webkidunia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4452974247948042517-account_id1.png";s:11:"testimonial";s:315:"WebKiDuniya gave my business the most needed push. Their eye-catching advertisement design appealed the customer in a positive manner. Their facebook promotions targeted the most appropriate audience flooding us with customer queries. Plus they are never annoyed with my frequent question answer sessions with them.";s:8:"btn_text";s:30:"Director - Aplus, ASOP Limited";s:7:"btn_url";s:20:"http://www.aplus.in/";}i:13;a:5:{s:5:"title";s:16:"Rtn. Navin Nahar";s:6:"avatar";s:84:"http://webkidunia.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5973492108863517918-account_id1.png";s:11:"testimonial";s:357:"Rotary was always in need to get themselves on the World Wide Web. We were just searching for the most appropriate team. And our search ends with WebKiDuniya. Although we were quite unsure coz they were a newbie in the market but they are far better than we needed them to be. What astonish Rotary even more are their constant efforts towards being perfect.";s:8:"btn_text";s:48:"President - Rotary International Club Dewas 3040";s:7:"btn_url";s:26:"http://rotaryclubdewas.org";}}', 'yes'),
