(55, 1, '2017-01-20 17:58:59', '2017-01-20 17:58:59', 'Digital World. Digital Business. Digital Marketing. With each passing day the world is getting digitized and the audience exposed has certainly increased with that. The world is now at your finger tips. From shopping to paying your bills and getting acquainted with the products and services of industry or institution, the world has taken a huge leap towards digitization.\r\n\r\nTime changes everything. And if with changing time you couldn’t evolve, your existence is at risk. Digitization and turned world upside down. And surely that includes the change of advertising techniques. The tradition way of advertising has been taken down by the enhanced and improved DIGITAL MARKETING ideas.\r\n\r\n<strong>But what actually is digital marketing?</strong>\r\n\r\nDigital marketing is an umbrella term for the marketing of products or services using digital technologies, mainly on the Internet, but also including mobile phones, display advertising, and any other digital medium. On a simple tone, the advertisement or marketing of products and services on social media like Facebook, YouTube, Bulk SMS which does not deal in paper on a large scale is termed as Digital Marketing.\r\n\r\nBut what makes Digital Marketing a better choice over the traditional techniques and ways?\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Wider Market\r\nYou could reach better audience - the people who fall in your interest and are in need of your services.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ol start="2">\r\n 	<li>More Efficient\r\nDigital Marketing helps you reach the correct bunch of people who matches your advertise demand. And it gets you better efficiency.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ol start="3">\r\n 	<li>Vivid Customers\r\nThere are huge deal of customers available for your product. You could sit at a place and let your advertise travel the world and get you business.</li>\r\n 	<li>Easy &amp; Understandable\r\nThe Digital Market is easy and understandable.</li>\r\n 	<li>At Your Finger Tips\r\nEvery result to the promotion you made is just a click away from you. A closer analysis will show what you lack.</li>\r\n 	<li>Instant Response\r\nWhen your advertise reach the correct audience, the people who truly need your service, you are surely to get responded easily.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'How could digital marketing help my business grow?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-could-digital-marketing-help-my-business-grow', '', '', '2017-01-20 18:23:51', '2017-01-20 18:23:51', '', 0, 'http://webkidunia.com/?p=55', 0, 'post', '', 0),
