(58, 1, '2017-01-20 18:02:00', '2017-01-20 18:02:00', 'With each passing moment digital world seeks changes. The digital algorithm isn’t as easy as it looks and keeps on altering with time. The social marketing platform is always revealing something new each day, pay per click advertising brings out new results every time and search engines keeps on rolling update and the data is refreshed.\r\n\r\nReaching top isn’t as important as it is to stay at the top. And to help you evolve with the changing times and technologies you need to be updated about the techniques. Reading is the key to knowledge. These 8 blogs are well known for their trendy ways to keep up with industry news, changes, helpful guides and “how-to” posts. These online marketing blogs provide excellent content that every small business owner can benefit from reading.\r\n\r\n1. <a href="https://blog.google/">Google’s Official Blog</a>\r\n\r\nYou want to know what’s new with Google? Just sit back and go through the official blogs of Google. This is a must-read for anyone that wants to stay long. When any announcement is made here you know that it is 100% accurate and straight from the source. Google commands the biggest piece of the search engine pie so staying current on their latest products, culture and technology is a smart move.\r\n\r\n2. <a href="http://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/">Social Media Examiner</a>\r\n\r\nThere are loads of social media marketing bogs but Social Media Examiner is my preferred daily stop for my social fix. There are great articles with plenty of insight that cover all of the popular social media platforms. They have very strict publishing guidelines and their quality is always top notch.\r\n\r\n3. <a href="https://www.searchenginejournal.com/">Search Engine Journal</a>\r\n\r\nIf Search Engine Optimization is your lifeline, then Search Engine Journalhas to be your God Father. Search Engine Journal delivers a nice balance of SEO news as well as “how-to” posts that really provide their readers with helpful information.\r\n\r\n4. <a href="https://moz.com/blog">Moz Blog</a>\r\n\r\nWith over 10 years of SEO industry experience, Moz is a great daily read for search engine optimization tips, insight and discussion. The posts on the Moz blog are some of the most in-depth available, diving heavily into the technical aspect of SEO. Small business owners that are serious about learning how SEO really works should bookmark this blog and check-in on a regular basis.\r\n\r\n5. <a href="http://searchengineland.com/">Search Engine Land</a>\r\n\r\nThis is one of my favorite blogs to read for daily breaking news related to SEO. Updated several times throughout the day, Search Engine Land is usually the first search engine optimization media outlet to report on algorithm updates and other important news.\r\n\r\n6. <a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/">HubSpot Blog</a>\r\n\r\nThe HubSpot blog is, as they put it, “Your Daily Dose of Inbound.” This blog is a great source of marketing and sales information, all presented from an inbound marketing perspective. The HubSpot blog is constantly updated with new content throughout the day — and it is definitely a great source of information for small business owners.\r\n\r\n7. <a href="https://searchenginewatch.com/">Search Engine Watch</a>\r\n\r\nSearch Engine Watch is a great daily reader, as it features some very insightful SEO and PPC posts from industry experts. Several of the contributing authors featured on Search Engine Watch are in-house online marketing experts for some of the biggest brands in the world.\r\n\r\n8. <a href="https://www.marketingprofs.com/marketing/library">MarketingProfs</a>\r\n\r\nThis is the perfect combination of everything you need. It contains the tiniest details you require to start your digital business and develop into a huge one later. From advertising and email marketing to brand and career management MarketingProfs has everything for you.', '8 lessons to learn before you own a business', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '8-lessons-to-learn-before-you-own-a-business', '', '', '2017-01-20 18:21:25', '2017-01-20 18:21:25', '', 0, 'http://webkidunia.com/?p=58', 0, 'post', '', 0),
